Critical rules:

- Read the old source files for complete implementation logic. strategy.py is ~3,600 lines — port it faithfully, don’t simplify
- All DB queries must reference btc15m_* tables
- Config reads go through platform db.get_plugin_config(“btc_15m”) or db.get_config(“btc_15m.key”)
- Plugin state goes through db.get_plugin_state(“btc_15m”) / db.update_plugin_state(“btc_15m”, {…})
- python3 -m py_compile every file before moving on
- Observatory: quality tags on ALL observations, never silently drop
- Simulation: absolute timing, spread-based slippage, two-snapshot fill delay, FDR correction
- Time-weighted metrics: 14-day half-life exponential decay
- Fee resilience: skip strategies that don’t survive fee buffer

